snippet.title: The Binding of Isaac: Repentance New Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to PC and console in 2021, The Binding of Isaac: Repentance is the ultimate edition of the genre-defining twin-stick-shooter/ roguelike, with OVER 500 HOURS of new gameplay!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1426300/The_Binding_of_Isaac_Repentance/
